## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some sources may not reflect the most current research or trends in social media usage. Additionally, the report focuses primarily on the negative aspects of social media, which may not provide a balanced view of its potential benefits. Further research could explore the positive impacts of social media to provide a more comprehensive analysis.

